  "title": "✈️(TRAVEL OPPS)(FRESH GRADS)💥SALES AND MARKETING WARRIORS🔥",
  "description": "<p>Not a desk job. Not a “stare at screen all day” role.<br />This is for people who like being out, meeting others, and learning by doing 👀🔥</p><p>At <strong>Thrive Organization</strong>, we work on the ground with brands through face-to-face marketing. If you’re social, active, and want real experience (not just theory), this one’s for you.</p><p><strong>What You’ll Be Doing 🚀</strong><br />• Talking to customers & sharing product info 🗣️<br />• Running booths, roadshows & pop-ups 🎪<br />• Working with a tight-knit team 👊<br />• Picking up communication & sales skills fast 📢</p><p><strong>Who This Is For 🌱</strong><br />• Fresh grads or early-career starters 🎓<br />• People who enjoy moving around 💪<br />• Confident communicators (or want to be) 😄<br />• Learners with good vibes & energy ⚡</p><p><strong>What You’ll Get ✨</strong><br />• Full-time role with training 📚<br />• Young, fun, supportive team 🤜🤛<br />• Skills you can use anywhere 🧠</p><p>If you want a role that’s active, social, and helps you grow fast — apply and come thrive with <strong>Thrive Organization</strong> 🚀</p>",
